Royal Navy girls awesome?

244
00:16:07,049 --> 00:16:10,803
[CLEVELAND gasps, yelps]

245
00:16:10,845 --> 00:16:11,846
[ALL]
Hm?

246
00:16:11,888 --> 00:16:14,515
[CLEVELAND] She really
wasn't wearing any...

247
00:16:14,557 --> 00:16:16,184
[EDINBURGH chuckles]

248
00:16:16,225 --> 00:16:18,394
[AKASHI sighs]
A hot spring soak

249
00:16:18,436 --> 00:16:22,857
after work makes me feel
like one divine feline!

250
00:16:22,899 --> 00:16:25,818
[QUEEN ELIZABETH giggles]
A thermae bath

251
00:16:25,860 --> 00:16:28,488
hand‐built by us,
the Royal Navy!

252
00:16:28,529 --> 00:16:32,366
Hot springs aren't exclusive to
Sakura Empire, my dear!

253
00:16:32,408 --> 00:16:34,619
It's quite impressive,
Your Majesty.

254
00:16:43,503 --> 00:16:44,670
[JAVELIN]
Huh?

255
00:16:47,632 --> 00:16:50,384
[JAVELIN gasps] Unicorn,
you're very well‐endowed!

256
00:16:50,426 --> 00:16:52,595
[UNICORN gasps]

257
00:16:52,637 --> 00:16:53,930
[JAVELIN, LAFFEY]
Hm?

258
00:16:56,891 --> 00:16:58,768
[JAVELIN gasps] Oh no!
What's wrong, darling?

259
00:16:58,809 --> 00:17:01,395
Please don't cry!

260
00:17:01,437 --> 00:17:04,148
[UNICORN sobs]

261
00:17:04,190 --> 00:17:08,236
[UNICORN] I'm so small,
but my body looks like this.

262
00:17:08,277 --> 00:17:12,031
I'm afraid there's something
wrong with me.

263
00:17:12,073 --> 00:17:14,408
Oh my, I promise that's
not true at all.

264
00:17:14,450 --> 00:17:16,786
[UNICORN sobs]

265
00:17:16,827 --> 00:17:17,828
[JAVELIN exhales]

266
00:17:17,870 --> 00:17:22,291
Unicorn. Your body is great
and you're awesome.

267
00:17:22,333 --> 00:17:24,627
[UNICORN]
You don't mean that.

268
00:17:24,669 --> 00:17:25,878
Of course I do.

269
00:17:25,920 --> 00:17:27,964
[UNICORN gasps]
But I...

270
00:17:28,005 --> 00:17:31,133
I don't look the same
as everybody else.

271
00:17:31,175 --> 00:17:33,386
Everyone is different.
That's normal.

272
00:17:33,427 --> 00:17:34,887
[JAVELIN]
Mm‐hm.

273
00:17:34,929 --> 00:17:37,223
There's nothing wrong
with any body.

274
00:17:37,265 --> 00:17:40,351
[gasps]

275
00:17:40,393 --> 00:17:42,270
So it's okay?

276
00:17:42,311 --> 00:17:43,688
[JAVELIN gasps]

277
00:17:43,729 --> 00:17:44,855
[UNICORN]
Hm?

278
00:17:58,995 --> 00:18:00,913
[gasps]

279
00:18:04,250 --> 00:18:08,796
[gasps]
Maybe... yeah.

280
00:18:13,968 --> 00:18:15,261
[ILLUSTRIOUS gasps]

281
00:18:17,847 --> 00:18:18,931
[ILLUSTRIOUS giggles]

282
00:18:18,973 --> 00:18:22,560
[PRINCE OF WALES] Mm? You look
rather pleased about something.

283
00:18:22,602 --> 00:18:25,479
Yes, very much.

284
00:18:25,521 --> 00:18:29,066
[UNICORN, JAVELIN giggle]

285
00:18:55,509 --> 00:18:58,846
[UNICORN] Ayanami?
That girl we met before?

286
00:18:58,888 --> 00:19:02,933
[JAVELIN] Mm. We're supposed
to be her enemies.

287
00:19:02,975 --> 00:19:05,936
So this could be
very wrong, but...

288
00:19:07,855 --> 00:19:10,316
[JAVELIN]
I don't want to give up on her.

289
00:19:10,358 --> 00:19:14,403
Truth is... I still want to
be friends with Ayanami!

290
00:19:15,696 --> 00:19:17,740
[UNICORN]
Mm! I do, too.

291
00:19:17,782 --> 00:19:20,493
I want to see her again
and get to know her.

292
00:19:20,534 --> 00:19:23,287
I don't think it's fair that we
have to fight her like this.

293
00:19:23,329 --> 00:19:26,874
Same here. And we haven't
started any fights yet.

294
00:19:26,916 --> 00:19:29,502
[gasps]

295
00:19:29,543 --> 00:19:31,253
[LAFFEY exhales]

296
00:19:31,295 --> 00:19:32,755
[UNICORN]
Hm!

297
00:19:45,518 --> 00:19:49,271
[YORKTOWN] I have faith that
one day you'll remember.

298
00:19:49,313 --> 00:19:52,274
So many people have placed
their trust in your name.

299
00:20:08,249 --> 00:20:11,544
Good evening, Enterprise.
Having trouble sleeping?

300
00:20:11,585 --> 00:20:14,046
I felt the ocean
calling out to me.

301
00:20:14,088 --> 00:20:15,923
[BELFAST]
Huh?

302
00:20:15,965 --> 00:20:17,675
I'm joking.

303
00:20:17,717 --> 00:20:20,302
That seems quite
unlike you, doesn't it?

304
00:20:20,344 --> 00:20:25,349
It is. Maybe I'm just feeling
a little emotional right now.

305
00:20:25,391 --> 00:20:28,185
[BELFAST] Try and keep
yourself warm out here.

306
00:20:29,520 --> 00:20:32,690
You brought coffee?
At this hour of the night?

307
00:20:34,900 --> 00:20:36,777
[giggles]

308
00:20:38,654 --> 00:20:42,032
[gasps]
Thought you taught elegance.

309
00:20:52,501 --> 00:20:54,462
It's very quiet.

310
00:20:54,503 --> 00:20:55,838
Yes.

311
00:20:57,757 --> 00:21:00,509
[ENTERPRISE]
I never mind a quiet ocean.

312
00:21:11,896 --> 00:21:15,149
[PRINZ EUGEN] How pretty.
Must be Akagi's taste.

313
00:21:15,191 --> 00:21:16,650
[KAGA]
You're not welcome here.

314
00:21:16,692 --> 00:21:18,110
[PRINZ EUGEN]
Oh, come now.

315
00:21:18,152 --> 00:21:20,404
Let me join you
for just one drink.

316
00:21:20,446 --> 00:21:23,657
[KAGA] I decline.
You'll ruin the taste.

317
00:21:23,699 --> 00:21:24,784
[PRINZ EUGEN chuckles]

318
00:21:24,825 --> 00:21:27,703
