Are you not at all worried?

320
00:21:32,416 --> 00:21:34,502
What are you and
your sister scheming?

321
00:21:34,543 --> 00:21:37,087
I'm sorry, but that's
none of your concern.

322
00:21:37,129 --> 00:21:39,757
[PRINZ EUGEN]
Are you sure you and Akagi...

323
00:21:39,799 --> 00:21:43,010
