after the same thing?

324
00:21:43,052 --> 00:21:45,971
[KAGA growls]
That's enough from you!

325
00:21:50,017 --> 00:21:54,438
[PRINZ EUGEN] One‐sided love can
be so painful, don't you think?

326
00:21:54,480 --> 00:21:58,067
[PRINZ EUGEN] <i>Guten nacht.</i>
Have a pleasant night.

327
00:21:58,108 --> 00:21:59,443
[grunts]

328
00:22:05,783 --> 00:22:09,912
[AKAGI] Soon, we'll meet
again very soon.

329
00:22:11,872 --> 00:22:14,500
[AKAGI]
My dear sister Amagi.

